import { Row, Col } from 'antd';

ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <Row>
      <Col span={24}>col</Col>
    </Row>
    <Row>
      <Col span={12}>col-12</Col>
      <Col span={12}>col-12</Col>
    </Row>
    <Row>
      <Col span={8}>col-8</Col>
      <Col span={8}>col-8</Col>
      <Col span={8}>col-8</Col>
    </Row>
    <Row>
      <Col span={6}>col-6</Col>
      <Col span={6}>col-6</Col>
      <Col span={6}>col-6</Col>
      <Col span={6}>col-6</Col>
    </Row>
  </>,
  mountNode,
);
